    <body><p><span rend="main_text" rendition="div"><lb />
<span rend="jisage_3" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 3em">猶南町<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">むば</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（乳母）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>にもよろしく御伝へ御たのみ申あげ候。</span>
御文難<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>有、然ニ御<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">ちうもん</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（注文）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>の銀の板うちの<span type="ruby"><span type="rb">かんざし</span><span type="rp">（</span><span type="rt">（簪）</span><span type="rp">）</span></span>と云ものに、京打、江戸打と云あり、板打中にも色々の通り在<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>之、画図でも御こしなれバ、わかり可<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>申候。然りといへども後便ニ一つさし出し可<span rend="kaeriten" rendition="sub">レ</span>申と存じ候。御まち、かしこ。<lb />
<span rend="jisage_2" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 2em">三月廿四日<span rend="chitsuki_3" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 3em">龍</span></span>
<span rend="jisage_1" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 1em">呈　ふぐの春猪様</span>
<span rend="jisage_8" rendition="div" style="margin-left: 8em">御前へ<span rend="chitsuki_2" rendition="div" style="text-align:right; margin-right: 2em">龍馬</span></span>
<lb />
<lb />
<lb />
</span></p></body>
